###  Small Survey program                                                                                          ### 
###  Programmed by Mohannad Zalloom                                                                                ###
###                                                                                                                ###
###                                                                                                                ###
### This is simple program which make some surveys on Stores record                                                ###
### Who it works :                                                                                                 ###
###                                                                                                                ###
### First you need to send 'Help' message                                                                          ###
### Then you will receive a message tells you to enter the information about you to be stored in the System        ###
### but you need to be careful when sending data (send it in the right order) .                                    ###
###                                                                                                                ###
### Features :                                                                                                     ###
### 'Find' function searchs the stored records and display the profile for the person if its stored .              ###
### 'stat' function gives small statistics about the no of stored profiles.                                        ###
###                                                                                                                ###
###                                                                                                                ###
### END                                                                                                            ###